\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's World Championships\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"gender eligibility tests\", \"from\": 705, \"to\": 729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But no concrete proof has been given, while the IBA was expelled last year over financial and corruption concerns by theInternational Olympic Committee(IOC), which is overseeing boxing atParis2024.\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9994234777090901, \"rank\": 0.0005768257789141609, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 884, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1694077042774258e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no concrete proof\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 753}, {\"ngram\": \"financial and corruption concerns\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"atParis2024\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif and Lin are into the gold medal matches in their respective weight categories but the issue has mushroomed to the extent former US President Donald Trump and author JK Rowling have weighed in.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1066, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"US President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"score\": 0.9999990399615005, \"rank\": 9.179057970388989e-07, \"text\": \"Donald Trump\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Donald_Trump\"}, {\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"JK Rowling\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 937}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 942, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"the gold medal matches\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 977}, {\"ngram\": \"their respective weight categories\", \"from\": 981, \"to\": 1015}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"the extent\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two of Lin's most recent opponents have made 'X' symbols with their index fingers in the ring after their defeats, which is thought to be a reference to female XX chromosomes.\", \"from\": 1132, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1292, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999991241566, \"rank\": 8.757871226162976e-10, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lin's most recent opponents\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"X' symbols\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1188}, {\"ngram\": \"their index fingers\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1213}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1225}, {\"ngram\": \"their defeats\", \"from\": 1232, \"to\": 1245}, {\"ngram\": \"a reference\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1281}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But IOC president Bach reiterated his support for Khelif and Lin, as he said: \\\"This is not a question of inclusion, this has never played a role in all this, this is a question of justice: women must be allowed to take part in women's competitions.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1694077042774258e-27, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1327, \"end\": 1331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"score\": 0.9999999988772288, \"rank\": 1.1229036881371953e-09, \"text\": \"Bach\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johann_Sebastian_Bach\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his support\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1354}, {\"ngram\": \"Khelif\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"Lin\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"a question\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1423}, {\"ngram\": \"a role\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"a question\", \"from\": 1475, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1496}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1532}, {\"ngram\": \"women's competitions\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And the two are women.\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is not as easy (as those) in this cultural war may want to portray it, that the XX or XY is the clear distinction between men and women.\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1666, \"end\": 1668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999991241566, \"rank\": 8.757871226162976e-10, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}, {\"begin\": 1672, \"end\": 1674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.6976623582413582, \"rank\": 0.4333546182630828, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this cultural war\", \"from\": 1615, \"to\": 1632}, {\"ngram\": \"the clear distinction\", \"from\": 1678, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1708, \"to\": 1711}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This is scientifically not true anymore.\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1765, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Therefore these two are women and they have the right to participate in the women's competition.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 1810, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's competition\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has nothing to do with inclusion in any way.\\\"\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1911}]}, {\"sente